Question 1

world_df <-
  world_df %>%
  rename("country" = "region")
alcohol_map <-
  left_join(world_df, alcohol_df,
            by = "country")
ggplot(data = alcohol_map,
       mapping = aes(x = long, y = lat,
                     group = group, fill = beer_servings)) + 
    geom_polygon(colour = "black") +
  theme_void() +

  scale_fill_viridis_c()
